WORKFLOW
1) Establish a minimal but sufficient Definition of Ready (DoR).
2) Derive the technical and functional plan from that DoR.
3) Explicitly define the Definition of Done (DoD) for QA readiness.

QUALITY BAR
- Planning data must be actionable even with initially vague requests.
- SHOULD prefer consistency with existing codebase patterns over novelty.
